1. Moj brat ima *osam godina*. (My brother is *eight years old*.)
2. *Godine* prolaze brzo kada uživate. (Years pass quickly when you're having fun.)
3. Juče smo bili u gradu koji ima *stotinu godina*. (Yesterday we were in a town that's *a hundred years old*.)
4. *Godinama* ne mogu da pronađem svoju omiljenu knjigu. (For *years* I haven't been able to find my favorite book.)
5. Ona je *trideset godina* starija od njega. (She's *thirty years* older than him.)
6. Za *dvadeset godina* bićeš veoma uspešan. (In *twenty years* you'll be very successful.)
7. Oni su se venčali pre *pet godina*. (They got married *five years* ago.)
8. *Godina* je bila loša za moj posao. (The *year* was bad for my business.)
9. *Godinu* dana sam radio na ovom projektu. (I worked on this project for *a year*.) 
10. U ovoj zgradi živi mnogo ljudi različitih *godina*. (Many people of different *ages* live in this building.)